### Create an isolation segment

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/isolation_segments" \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
  -H "Content-type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "my_segment"
  }'
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :single_isolation_segment %>
```

#### Definition
`POST /v3/isolation_segments`

#### Required Parameters

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
**name** | _string_ | Name of the Isolation Segment.  Isolation Segment names must be unique across the entire system, and case is ignored when checking for uniqueness.

